com.yolanda.nohttp.rest

枚举 CacheMode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CacheMode>
      • com.yolanda.nohttp.rest.CacheMode
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Serializable, Comparable<CacheMode>

    public enum CacheMode
extends Enum<CacheMode>

    NoHttp caching pattern, the default value is DEFAULT, other value may be REQUEST_NETWORK_FAILED_READ_CACHE, ONLY_READ_CACHE, ONLY_REQUEST_NETWORK, NONE_CACHE_REQUEST_NETWORK.

    Created in 2016/3/20 23:17.
    作者:
    Yan Zhenjie.

    • 枚举常量概要

      枚举常量 
      枚举常量和说明
      DEFAULT
      The default mode, according to the standard HTTP protocol cache, such as response header is 304.
      NONE_CACHE_REQUEST_NETWORK
      If there is no cache request, it returns the cache cache exists.
      ONLY_READ_CACHE
      If the cache exists invoke OnResponseListener.onSucceed(int, Response), otherwise invoke OnResponseListener.onFailed(int, String, Object, Exception, int, long).
      ONLY_REQUEST_NETWORK
      It does not deal with anything related to the cache, only to get the data from the network.
      REQUEST_NETWORK_FAILED_READ_CACHE
      Request fails to read the cache, if the request to the server success or cache exists invoke OnResponseListener.onSucceed(int, Response), if the request to the server failure or cache does not exist invoke OnResponseListener.onFailed(int, String, Object, Exception, int, long).
